name: Michael Brown
summary: Senior Product Manager at Enterprise Corp, leading cross-functional teams to deliver SaaS solutions.
long_summary: Michael Brown has over 8 years in product management, specializing in B2B SaaS platforms. He excels at defining product roadmaps, coordinating engineering and design teams, and driving user adoption. His notable achievements include a 40% increase in user engagement and a 25% reduction in churn rates.

education.institution: University of Chicago Booth School of Business
